text: Selma Kajan (born 30 July 1991) is an Australian athlete who specialises in middle-distance running. She qualified for the 2016 Summer Olympics. Kajan has competed at the IAAF World Youth Championships. In 2012, she graduated from University of New South Wales. == Personal bests == === Outdoor === {| class="wikitable" |- ! Event !! Record !!
